{
  "video_id": "4R3gFN8sUa8",
  "title": "What the Russian Revolution would have looked like on social media | Mikhail Zygar",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13930.0,
      "end_time": 14243.0,
      "text": "What is history?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15438.0,
      "end_time": 17960.0,
      "text": "It is something written by the winners."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20203.0,
      "end_time": 24951.0,
      "text": "There is a stereotype that history should be focused on the rulers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24975.0,
      "end_time": 26671.0,
      "text": "like Lenin or Trotsky."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27445.0,
      "end_time": 30765.0,
      "text": "As a result, people in many countries, like mine, Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31932.0,
      "end_time": 35409.0,
      "text": "look at history as something that was predetermined"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35433.0,
      "end_time": 37162.0,
      "text": "or determined by the leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38750.0,
      "end_time": 40737.0,
      "text": "and common people could not influence it in any way."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41585.0,
      "end_time": 45165.0,
      "text": "Many Russians today do not believe that Russia could ever have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45189.0,
      "end_time": 48200.0,
      "text": "or ever will be a truly democratic nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50987.0,
      "text": "and this is due to the way history has been framed"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51110.0,
      "end_time": 52582.0,
      "text": "to the citizens of Russia."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52606.0,
      "end_time": 54184.0,
      "text": "And this is not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55110.0,
      "end_time": 60772.0,
      "text": "To prove it, I spent two years of my life trying to go 100 years back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60796.0,
      "end_time": 63138.0,
      "text": "to the year 1917,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63162.0,
      "end_time": 65615.0,
      "text": "the year of the Russian Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65639.0,
      "end_time": 71345.0,
      "text": "I asked myself, what if the internet and Facebook existed 100 years ago?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72155.0,
      "end_time": 77446.0,
      "text": "So last year, we built a social network for dead people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77470.0,
      "end_time": 79858.0,
      "text": "named Project1917.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 82111.0,
      "end_time": 84683.0,
      "text": "My team and I created our software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84707.0,
      "end_time": 89987.0,
      "text": "digitized and uploaded all possible real diaries and letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90110.0,
      "end_time": 93113.0,
      "text": "written by more than 3,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93137.0,
      "end_time": 94669.0,
      "text": "100 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94693.0,
      "end_time": 98435.0,
      "text": "So any user of our website or application"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 98459.0,
      "end_time": 102460.0,
      "text": "can follow a news feed for each day of 1917"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 102484.0,
      "end_time": 106604.0,
      "text": "and read what people like Stravinsky or Trotsky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 106629.0,
      "end_time": 110176.0,
      "text": "Lenin or Pavlova and others thought and felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110931.0,
      "end_time": 115636.0,
      "text": "We watch all those personalities being ordinary people like you and me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 115660.0,
      "end_time": 117572.0,
      "text": "not demigods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117596.0,
      "end_time": 124580.0,
      "text": "and we see that history consists of their mistakes, fears, weaknesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 124604.0,
      "end_time": 127357.0,
      "text": "not only their \"genius ideas.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 128643.0,
      "end_time": 130842.0,
      "text": "Our project was a shock for many Russians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 130866.00000000001,
      "end_time": 136467.0,
      "text": "who used to think that our country has always been an autocratic empire"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 136491.0,
      "end_time": 139904.0,
      "text": "and the ideas of freedom and democracy could never have prevailed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 139928.0,
      "end_time": 142578.0,
      "text": "just because democracy was not our destiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143514.0,
      "end_time": 145442.0,
      "text": "But if we take a broader look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 146291.0,
      "end_time": 147879.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not that black and white."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 149771.0,
      "end_time": 154474.0,
      "text": "Yes, 1917 led to 70 years of communist dictatorship."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 155584.0,
      "end_time": 160233.0,
      "text": "But with this project, we see that Russia could have had a different history"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 160257.0,
      "end_time": 164297.0,
      "text": "and a democratic future, as any other country could or still can."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 165249.0,
      "end_time": 169660.0,
      "text": "Reading the posts from 1917,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 169900.0,
      "end_time": 172570.0,
      "text": "you learn that Russia was the first country in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172810.0,
      "end_time": 174170.0,
      "text": "to abolish the death penalty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 174410.0,
      "end_time": 178215.0,
      "text": "or one of the first ones to grant women voting rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 179334.0,
      "end_time": 185559.0,
      "text": "Knowing history and understanding how ordinary people influenced history"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 185583.0,
      "end_time": 187441.0,
      "text": "can help us create a better future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 187465.0,
      "end_time": 191209.0,
      "text": "because history is just a rehearsal of what&#39;s happening right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 192500.0,
      "end_time": 195413.0,
      "text": "We do need new ways of telling history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 195437.0,
      "end_time": 197800.0,
      "text": "and this year, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 197320.0,
      "end_time": 202873.0,
      "text": "we started a new online project that is called 1968Digital.com,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 203681.0,
      "end_time": 208506.0,
      "text": "and that is an online documentary series"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 208530.0,
      "end_time": 212474.0,
      "text": "that gives you an impression of that year, 1968,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 212498.0,
      "end_time": 216360.0,
      "text": "a year marked by global social change"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 216610.0,
      "end_time": 219771.0,
      "text": "that, in many ways, created the world as we know it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 220327.0,
      "end_time": 223437.0,
      "text": "But we are making that history alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 223461.0,
      "end_time": 228000.0,
      "text": "by imagining what if all the main characters could use mobile phones ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 229299.0,
      "end_time": 230449.0,
      "text": "just like that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 231906.0,
      "end_time": 236207.0,
      "text": "And we see that a lot of individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 237477.0,
      "end_time": 242725.0,
      "text": "were facing the same challenges and were fighting for the same values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 242749.0,
      "end_time": 247146.0,
      "text": "no matter if they lived in the US or in USSR"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 247170.0,
      "end_time": 250900.0,
      "text": "or in France or in China or in Czechoslovakia."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 251345.0,
      "end_time": 254187.0,
      "text": "By exposing history in such a democratic way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 254211.0,
      "end_time": 255604.0,
      "text": "through social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 256762.0,
      "end_time": 261983.0,
      "text": "we show that people in power are not the only ones making choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 262596.0,
      "end_time": 266334.0,
      "text": "That gives any user a possibility of reclaiming history."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 267191.0,
      "end_time": 268445.0,
      "text": "Ordinary people matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 269960.0,
      "end_time": 270350.0,
      "text": "They have an impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 271476.0,
      "end_time": 272627.0,
      "text": "Ideas matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 273471.0,
      "end_time": 277827.0,
      "text": "Journalists, scientists, philosophers matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 278542.0,
      "end_time": 279914.0,
      "text": "We shape society."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 280789.0,
      "end_time": 282522.0,
      "text": "We all make history."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 283436.0,
      "end_time": 284587.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 284611.0,
      "end_time": 288380.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}